teamcardone.name: Omowumi Adekoya
teamcardone.text: In my spare time, I enjoy reading novels.

teamcardtwo.name: Damilola Obidairo
teamcardtwo.text: I create time to intellectually debate with my family. I destress by listening to music or creating music with my voice and guitars. It gives me a lot of pleasure and satisfaction to garden and see my plants grow slowly and suddenly. In my spare time, I engage with thought-provoking books and epic/sci-fi movies.

teamcardthree.name: Abiola Oreagba
teamcardthree.text: I am a fun-loving, process-driven person who enjoys reading and dancing. I am a certified foodie and an Arsenal fan.

teamcardfour.name: Dr. Seun Oladele
teamcardfour.text: Music is what I love to do. That’s the only fun thing I know. I play video games a lot and watch movies a lot. For someone considered a researcher, I do not really like reading.

teamcardfive.name: Opeyemi Bioku
teamcardfive.text: Enjoying good music across many genres as well as movies in my leisure is my favorite thing to do.

teamcardsix.name: Motunrayo Dasilva
teamcardsix.text: When i am not working, I enjoy spending quality time with my family, the satisfaction that comes with it is everything. I also enjoy acting, feel free to call me a drama queen.

teamcardseven.name: Aisha Adeleke
teamcardseven.text: I have always wanted to have a Tiger as a pet because I find the fur prints attractive and I also love cat families, but I got a cat because I can't have a tiger.

teamcardeight.name: Adam Yakub
teamcardeight.text: As early as 6a.m, I’m always at the football pitch every Saturday.
